      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You seriously have to see this beauty to believe it! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s honestly still in showroom condition\u2014not a single scratch or smudge in sight. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that wonderful fresh-car feel. I'm looking for a new home for it where it'll be just as loved. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin or have any questions at all! \u2728",
