      "description": "Presented is a pristine E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. Power is derived from the S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. This example boasts a bulletproofed double-VANOS system and reinforced rear subframe mounting points, addressing critical preventative maintenance. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise throws, paired with a limited-slip differential for exceptional mechanical grip. The factory finish is concours-level, free of imperfections, while the undercarriage remains remarkably clean, reflecting its history in a climate-controlled environment. A true turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
